    "title_en": "Charge functions for all dimensional partitions",
    "abstract_en": "The charge functions for n-dimensional partitions are known for n=2,3,4 in the literature. In a recent work, we gave the expression for arbitrary odd dimension; here we further conjecture a formula for all even-dimensional cases. This conjecture is proved rigorously for 6D, and numerically verified for 8D.",
